  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study examines the efficacy of haldol versus risperdal in the treatment of aggression in
      psychotic prison inmates. It is hypothsized that risperdal will be more effective in
      decreasing aggression than haldol.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
